>You shift expired boxes of candy and moldy bread aside as you search the shelves of the gas station.

>Ya know, this would be a beautiful day if it wasn't for the distant gunfire and smoke plumes from the active warzone you're surviving in.
>As you walk towards the tree line to head back to your hide out, automatic gunfire rings out.
>You panic and nearly American history X yourself on the curb as bullets snap and ping off the buildings and wrecked cars behind you.
>Boots stomping and adrenaline pumping, you dive behind a black SUV and fumble with your M4.
>A man in the distance is screaming bloody murder as a feminine shriek accompanies it.
>You peak over the hood of the car and see a horrific sight.
>A group of Scavs and what you can only assume are Ex-BEARs are running full sprint after a young wolf girl.

>There's at least 6 of them.
>And they're heading straight for you.
>You mount your gun on the hood of the car and wait for the right moment.
>As the wolf gets closer, you can see her face much clearer.
>Utter terror and fear.
